This is a school project, a  Appcelerator Titanium Mobile Project.
Author collaboration: Glenn Billiau @billiauglenn & Vicent Van Grootel @vanbiggels

This project has a Drupal 7 backend for users and nodes.

Features:

register a user to drupal - bugged: submitted password to drupal is incorrect, users can't loggin.
login a user from drupal - due to bugged user reg, try defeault account: 'userfoo:passbar'
mapview with current location - local nodes are no yet supported
creat a new node + take a camera picture, uploading picture is not yet supported.
view datalist from recent nodes + search
detail view from selected node: view author, body and comment count.

